{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HV6VoJoLsLTyS6cTH3RQLd","type":"tool_result","content":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz Information\n\n**Location:** Saint-Jorioz (commune in Haute-Savoie)\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach features variable pricing - it is \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" (paid entry July-August at €2.60, free rest of year).\n\n**Direct Link:** https://loisirs74.fr/cs/plage-de-saint-jorioz\n\n**Description:** This is a large natural sandy beach on Lac d'Annecy with views of Dents de Lanfon, awarded Blue Flag status."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"627e56e9-f549-4562-8138-7a88a71c466a","uuid":"dd4708d7-1cb2-45cf-b394-62933013af09","timestamp":"2026-07-05T21:55:51.872Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":160440,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Plage de Saint-Jorioz Information\n\n**Location:** Saint-Jorioz (commune in Haute-Savoie)\n\n**Entrance Fee:** The beach features variable pricing - it is \"Placený vstup v červenci a srpnu (2,60 €), zbytek roku zdarma\" (paid entry July-August at €2.60, free rest of year).\n\n**Direct Link:** https://loisirs74.fr/cs/plage-de-saint-jorioz\n\n**Description:** This is a large natural sandy beach on Lac d'Annecy with views of Dents de Lanfon, awarded Blue Flag status.","durationMs":3737,"url":"https://loisirs74.fr/cs/"}}
